          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>2. Information on the Site</h2>
            <p>The information provided on this Site is general and should not be considered personal or professional advice. The Site and its content are provided "as is" without any guarantees. You use the Site at your own risk.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>3. Our Responsibility</h2>
            <p>We aim to ensure all information is accurate, relevant, and up to date. However, errors or omissions may occur, and we will correct them where possible.</p>
            <p>We take reasonable steps to keep the Site secure and operational, but we cannot guarantee uninterrupted access or protection from unauthorised interference.</p>
            <p>GBI Ventures Ltd will not be liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages (including loss of data, profit, or business). Nothing in this Legal Notice limits our liability for fraud or intentional misconduct.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>4. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p>This Site may contain links to third-party websites we do not control. We are not responsible for their content, accuracy, or availability, nor for any damages arising from their use.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>All text, images, videos, and audio on this Site are the property of GBI Ventures Ltd and may not be reproduced without written permission. Our name, logo, products, and services are protected trademarks.</p>
            <p>This Site is governed by UK law.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>6. Personal Data</h2>
            <p>Any personal data collected through this Site is used solely to improve its technical functionality. Data is processed confidentially and in accordance with UK data protection laws.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>7. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
            <p>This Legal Notice is governed by the laws of England and Wales. Disputes will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in London, unless otherwise required by law.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>8. Severability</h2>
            <p>If any provision of this Legal Notice is found invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions will remain in full force and effect.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>9. Contact</h2>
            <p><strong>GBI Ventures Ltd</strong><br>
            8 Northumberland Avenue<br>
            WC2N 5BY London<br>
            United Kingdom<br>
            Company No. 15416150</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .breadcrumb-section {
    background: #FAFAFA;
    padding: 15px 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: #787878;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #469ADC;
  }

  .breadcrumb .current {
    color: #469ADC;
  }

  .breadcrumb .separator {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .page-section {
    background: #FAFAFA;
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #253461;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .content-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E8E8E8;
  }

  .legal-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #253461;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #5F5F5F;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  .legal-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .content-card {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
